</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check if green led V3 is on 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The internal generated power supplies on IOBOARD_DRAWER are within specification when the led is on. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check the +24VL connection (X67-p2,p1) to IOBOARD_DRAWER and power supply 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="21ELEC01" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-F5A56C10-5F14-434F-BE74-69E7D5DBC19C.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>21 Control</xref> 
