</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect all harnesses except X67 and X84 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if problem caused by external fault (harness/pba) 
